ActNatural Sciences and Engineering Research Council Act
Financial Administration Act
SubjectOrder designating the Minister of Science, a member of the Queen’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the Natural Sciences and Engineering Research Council Act and as the appropriate Minister for the purposes of the Financial Administration Act
PrecisOrder (1) Repealing Order in Council P.C. 2017-74 of February 1, 2017d; (2) Designating the Minister of Science, a member of the Queen’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the NATURAL SCIENCES AND ENGINEERING RESEARCH COUNCIL ACT; and (3) Designating the Minister of Science as the appropriate Minister with respect to the Natural Sciences and Engineering Research Council for the purposes of the FINANCIAL ADMINISTRATION ACT.
